        name - (Required) User name
        password - (Required) User password
        email - (Required) email
        genre - (Required) User genre. V for man, H for woman and I when it's unknown
        partnerAlias - (Required) Partner alias (www for www.mundijuegos.com)
        ip - User ip
        country - Two letter iso country code
        friend - Username of the friend that suggested this registration
        additionalParams - json-code-key-valued-array with special params, for example campaign params (utm_medium, utm_term, utm_content, utm_campaign, utm_source, ..)

        User created data

      • registerOrLoginExternalUser

        public UserResponseData registerOrLoginExternalUser(java.lang.String providerName,
                                           java.lang.String providerUserId,
                                           java.lang.String email,
                                           java.lang.String genre,
                                           java.lang.String ip,
                                           java.lang.String name,
                                           java.lang.String password,
                                           java.lang.String country,
                                           java.lang.String partnerAlias,
                                           java.lang.String friend,
                                           java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> additionalParams,
                                           java.lang.String realName)
                                             throws ServiceDefinitionException,
                                                    ServiceInvocationException
        Links a user from an external site (for example, facebook). If the user has not been linked before, a new account at our side it's created. If not, the before created user reference is returned
        Parameters:
        providerName - (Required)Provider name. It must be facebook or taringa
        providerUserId - (Required) User id in the external system (in the case of facebook, user id)
        email - (Required) User email
        genre - (Required) User genre (V for man, H for woman, I for not defined yet)
        ip - (Required) User ip (number dotted string format)
        name - User desired name (5-15 letters and numbers string)
        password - User desired password
        country - two-letter iso country code
        partnerAlias - Alias of the partner (www by default)
        friend - User name from the friend that enrolled this user
        additionalParams - key-valued structure with special params : channel => ‘Facebook’, ‘Portal’, ‘IOS’, ‘Android’ game_id => Game id responsible for the user register bu_lang => user country in the ISO 3166 two letter country code utm_medium => utm campaign parameter utm_term => utm campaign parameter utm_source => utm campaign parameter utm_content => utm campaign parameter
        realName - User real name (for example: 'John Smith'). It helps to generate the user loginname, when is not possible to do it from his email
        Returns:
        User data
        Throws:
        ServiceDefinitionException
        ServiceInvocationException
